  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees C.",
    "For preparing the crust. Mix crumbs, sugar, salt, and cinnamon in a",
    "Add butter and egg white. Put crumb mixture in the up and bottom",
    "sides of a pie plate, and bake at 375 degrees C for around 9 minutes.",
    "Let it cool.",
    "For preparing the filling, mix ingredients in a bowl.",
    "Put milk in a saucepan over the medium heat. Gradually mix hot milk",
    "and egg mixture. Stir constantly.",
    "Put milk mixture back to the pan. Cook until it is thick. Stir",
    "constantly.",
    "Turn off the heat, then put chocolate in it. Stir smoothly.",
    "Let it cool, then put filling in the crust. Put plastic wrap to cover it.",
    "Chill for 3 hours, then take off the plastic wrap.",
    "Pour whipped topping, and sprinkle with cracker crumbs.",
    "Serve and enjoy!"
